{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1693-12_173","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Stances","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", décembre 1693 [tome 15], p. 173-176.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Nous sommes sur une matiere de Vers, &amp; elle me fait souvenir de vous envoyer ceux-cy, dont la maladie d’une fort aimable personne fait le sujet."],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"STANCES.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amour, peux-tu voir sans douleur","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’une maladie insolente","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ose accabler de sa rigueur","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cloris, dont la beauté naissante","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"T’a rendu maistre de mon cœur ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Peux-tu voir obscurcir ces yeux","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pleins de douceur &amp; de tendresse,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus brillans que l’Astre des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui te faisoient par la Jeunesse","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dresser des Autels en tous lieux ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Peux-tu voir, insensible Amour,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ternir l’éclat de ce visage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour qui chacun te fait la cour,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui paroist la vive image","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De celle qui t’a mis au jour ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Haste-toy de la secourir,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si tu veux défendre ta gloire.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En la laissant longtemps souffrir,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Renonce enfin à la Victoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu n’as plus rien à conquerir.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais si tu défens ses appas","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De toutes les douleurs cruelles","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui nous conduisent au trépas,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Devant toy les ames rebelles","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mettront toujours les armes bas.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Cloris a droit de tout charmer,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jadis Helene si vantée,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont les attraits firent armer","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toute l’Asie épouvantée,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne se faisoit pas tant aimer.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" On ne sçauroit blâmer Pâris","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’avoir toujours gardé sa proye,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy que sa mort en fust le prix,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais il estoit plus beau que Troye","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Perist pour défendre Cloris.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Viens donc luy donner un secours,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où ma tendresse te convie ;","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La mort ne peut finir le cours","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De sa belle &amp; charmante vie,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans terminer aussi mes jours.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}}]}}}